1"><h1>Desk Setup 2021</h1></a> <span style="position: relative; bottom:20px; display:block; font-size:.85em; color:var(--light-font-color);"><i>Mar 11, 2021</i></span><div style="border-left: .1rem solid; padding-left: 8px; border-color:var(--light-font-color);"><p>Full time remote-work has necessitated a serious home-workstation. This post is dedicated to the gear that is part of my setup.</div><div style="font-size:.85em; color:var(--light-font-color); font-style:italic; position:relative; bottom:10px;">#desksetup #technology #apple #desksetup</div></div><ul class="pagination pagination-sm" style="display: flex; justify-content:center;"><li><a href="/blogs/">&laquo;</a><li><a href="/blogs">&nbsp;First</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<li> <a href="/blogs">1</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;<li> 2 &nbsp;&nbsp;<li> <a href="/blogs/page/3" title="Blogs">3</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;<li><a href="/blogs/page/3/">Last (3)&nbsp;</a><li><a href="/blogs/page/3/">&raquo;</a></ul></main><aside class="container_item"></aside><footer class="container_item"> <center><span style="color:var(--light-font-color); font-size:.8em; font-style:italic; position:relative; top:25px;">Brought to you with <i class="ph-fill ph-heart-straight" style="color:var(--accent-color);"></i> by <a href="https://shellsharks.com/about">Shellsharks</a></span></center> <center> <img id="sharkfooter" src="/assets/img/sharks-circling.png" alt="Circling Sharks" style="width:150px;"></img> </center></footer></div><noscript><div class="panel" align="center" style="font-weight:bold;"><h1>Please enable JavaScript.</h1></div></noscript> <script src="/assets/js/themeswitcher.js"></script>
